STATE of North Carolina
v.
Troy Giles GADDY. No. 582P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Troy Giles Gaddy, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Kenneth W. Honeycutt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 16th day of November 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Union County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
